## Dependency Stack

| Layer | Library | Role |
|---|---|---|
| Data Engineering | `pandas`, `numpy` | DataFrame manipulation, vectorized feature injection |
| ML — Tabular | `xgboost`, `scikit-learn` | Gradient-boosted tree expert, preprocessing, evaluation |
| ML — NLP | `transformers` (HuggingFace) | CodeBERT tokenizer and encoder |
| DL Runtime | `torch` (PyTorch, CUDA) | Model training, GPU memory management, inference |
| Training UX | `tqdm` | Progress bars for epoch monitoring |
| Reproducibility | `random.seed(42)`, `np.random.seed(42)` | Deterministic dataset generation |

---

*This system represents a production-viable diagnostic architecture for CI/CD failure classification, combining structured and unstructured signals through a modality-decoupled, safety-gated Late Fusion Ensemble.*
